Most of Germany’s Idled Nuclear Plants Will Never Open, CDU's Groehe Says

-- B y   T o n y   C z u c z k a
-- 
2011-03-28T05:54:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/most-of-germany-s-idled-nuclear-plants-to-stay-shut-cdu-says.html
The majority of seven nuclear
German power plants idled during a three-month safety review by
 Chancellor Angela Merkel ’s government will probably never start
up again, Hermann Groehe, the general secretary of Merkel’s
 Christian Democratic Union , said. Groehe, in an interview on ARD
television today, didn’t specify which reactors may be shut
down.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tony Czuczka at 
